OL,3,CHow could Keir Starmer be replaced and
OL,4,Cwhat would be the next steps?
OL,6,FIt's clear from the prime minister's
OL,7,Fspeech today - if he is going to go,
OL,8,Fit won't be willingly.
OL,10,FDespite the loyal cabinet ministers
OL,11,Fand MPs, who turned up to applaud
OL,12,Fevery line, the latest attempt at a
OL,13,Freset has not stopped the number of
OL,14,Fbackbenchers turning against him
OL,15,Fcontinuing to tick up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
