OL,3,CHow could Keir Starmer be replaced and
OL,4,Cwhat would be the next steps?
OL,6,FITV News is tracking the views of
OL,7,FLabour MPs and currently more than 50
OL,8,Fare calling publicly for him to go,
OL,9,Fwith another eight saying he should
OL,10,Funless he can change course. But what
OL,11,Fthey can't agree on is whether the
OL,12,Fresponse to the current crisis should
OL,13,Fbe for their party to move to the left
OL,14,For the right, or even when to move.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
