OL,3,CHow could Keir Starmer be replaced and
OL,4,Cwhat would be the next steps?
OL,6,FThe little-known former minister
OL,7,FCatherine West briefly became the most
OL,8,Ftalked about women in politics when it
OL,9,Flooked as though she would attempt to
OL,10,Fforce a leadership contest. But today
OL,11,Fshe had second thoughts. She is now
OL,12,Fsaying she is just asking MPs about
OL,13,Fwhether they support a transition to a
OL,14,Fnew leader by September.
OL,16,FSo what could happen next?
OL,18,FOne of the frontrunners to take over
OL,19,Fcould decide the anti-Starmer
OL,20,Fgroundswell is becoming so great that
OL,21,Fthey need to declare their hand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
