OL,3,CHow could Keir Starmer be replaced and
OL,4,Cwhat would be the next steps?
OL,6,FTheir backers need to go public;
OL,7,Funlike the Conservatives, it's not a
OL,8,Fsecret ballot and the prime minister
OL,9,Fautomatically gets the right to fight
OL,10,Fthe contest.
OL,12,FOr the prime minister's cabinet could
OL,13,Fact. Boris Johnson's demise was sealed
OL,14,Fin 2022 when 30 of his ministers
OL,15,Fresigned. Keir Starmer's cabinet has
OL,16,Fbeen publicly supportive so far, some
OL,17,Fmore enthusiastically than others. If
OL,18,Fthe pressure intensifies, his cabinet
OL,19,For other party grandees could
OL,20,Fprivately urge the prime minister to
OL,21,Fset a timetable to step down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
