OL,3,CHow could Keir Starmer be replaced and
OL,4,Cwhat would be the next steps?
OL,6,FKeir Starmer is hoping the memory of
OL,7,Frecent political turbulence will shore
OL,8,Fup his position.
OL,10,FThe country lurched from Theresa May
OL,11,Fto Boris Johnson to Liz Truss to Rishi
OL,12,FSunak in the space of just five years.
OL,14,FKeir Starmer has been in the job 22
OL,15,Fmonths, and much of his party, like
OL,16,Fmuch of the country, has lost faith in
OL,17,Fhim, but he's digging in and there is
OL,18,Fno consensus on what to do about it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
